# AI Provider Layer

- Resolve models only through `lib/ai/provider.ts` — never hardcode provider URLs in routes.
- Priority: `OPENAI_API_KEY` → `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` → `GROQ_API_KEY`.
- Use `streamText()` from `ai` package; avoid hand-rolled SSE parsers in new code.
- Legacy `/api/chat` may still use Groq fetch — migrate to AI SDK when touching that file.
- Structured diagnosis advice: JSON with `personalizedAdvice`, `dailyTip`, `affirmation` + Zod validation.
- Always ship typed fallbacks when keys are missing or upstream fails.
